						<h1>Layout</h1>
						<div class="breakout">
							<p>MyService is developed to be mobile first. Layouts in MyService are built using UI-Kit's powerful 12-column grid system.
								The look and feel is then fine-tuned using media queries, based on a set of 4 breakpoints. This combination results
								in a consistent user experience across all devices.</p>
						</div>

						<h2>Grid system</h2>
						<p>The UI-Kit grid system is based on a 12 column layout and uses a series of containers, rows, and columns to layout
							and align content. The following table shows how the MyService grid system works across multiple devices.</p>
						<table class="table">
							<thead>
								<tr>
									<td></td>
									<td>
										<h4>Extra small</h4>
									</td>
